camping in the driveway at the mechanic's house.

> coil going bad: Runs fine, then sometimes looses power at higer
> RPM's and under load (going up a hill).  Then it will
> be fine again, run well for a while, then back to a
> lose of power at higher RPM's. Plus it will stall out
> when the it's acting up. All the lights and radio work
> fine. Starter cranking fine. The timing is fine. I've
> just had a tune up and the distributor rebuilt. These
